---

<section class="faq">
  <div class="faq-container">
    <h2 class="faq-title">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">Is it really free?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">Yes. 2 full tailoring sessions free, no card required. Upgrade to Pro for unlimited.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">How is this different from just using ChatGPT?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">JobTailor is purpose-built. No prompting skills needed — paste and go. You get structured output in 4 organized tabs, not a wall of text.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">Will this work for any job?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">Yes. The AI reads the specific job description you paste, not a generic template.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">Is my resume data stored?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">No. Your text is sent to our AI, processed, and returned. We don't store it.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary class="faq-question">What is an ATS score?</summary>
        <p class="faq-answer">ATS stands for Applicant Tracking System. Most large companies filter resumes automatically. Our score estimates how well your resume matches the job. It's an AI estimate, not a guarantee.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .faq-container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  .faq-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 56px;
    line-height: 64px;
    color: var(--forest);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .faq-list {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--cream2);
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream2);
  }

  .faq-question {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--forest);
    padding: 24px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    position: relative;
    padding-right: 32px;
  }

  .faq-question::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-question::after {
    content: "+";
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--muted);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .faq-question::after {
    content: "−";
  }

  .faq-answer {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 26px;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-bottom: 24px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq-title {
      font-size: 40px;
      line-height: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>
